Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:32.85,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:36.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:41.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:01.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:05.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:12.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:19.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:23.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:30.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:34.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:46.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:32.85,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:36.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}隨心所欲地去描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:41.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描繪的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}萬里無雲的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邊無際的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}純潔無瑕的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:01.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈著無限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:05.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於能自由翱翔於天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}長出了美麗的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:12.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無瑕的瞳孔在尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:19.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那無數的願望中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:23.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一個能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不願讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:30.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要緊緊抓住那夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:34.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描寫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:46.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈願的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1000,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}訣別
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:43.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:49.86,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:58.52,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:06.55,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:15.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:23.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:30.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:39.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:47.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:55.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:43.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:49.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤獨中尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:58.52,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用靈魂連結我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:06.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用愛戀溫暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:15.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那顫抖的祈願之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:23.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:30.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不斷交替的輪迴之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:39.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不終結的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:47.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不斷輪迴的 那些傳頌之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:55.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守護著安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們卡露拉阿滋雷的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯歐卡斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運送劍奴的貨船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到叛亂軍的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.14,0:01:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍奴都被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上開始準備討伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做好迎接你的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請快點來到我的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿露 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有討厭吃的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 沒有這事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 東霞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面沒有下毒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 給聖上的食物一定要先由在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝納威大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎在納˙托庫的劍奴發動了叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納˙托庫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得那裡應該是卡露拉原先所在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率領叛亂軍的似乎是一個叫做迪利霍萊的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於物資的嚴重不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛亂軍漸漸開始處於劣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事相求 所以來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿了不同的衣服給人的感覺也不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有事相求 穿正裝也是基本的禮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納˙托庫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入正題真快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話我也想幫點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會因此而讓這個國家捲入戰火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我不會自私到要你白白幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我的一切都奉獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 從每一根髮絲到每一滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂立「解放者」的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在說些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我讓你去死的話你真的會去死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是主人的願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有這樣的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就實現你的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約看來成立了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 和這個倒沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想白白接受恩惠喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我說過了身心都要奉獻給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了 哈克奧羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 能倒點茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺最近艾露露好像一直躲著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您心裡有沒有數呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅 情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說 情況不容樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在叛亂軍節節敗退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鎮壓應該只是時間上的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 正如你所聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再進一步的介入恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 身體不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 已經醒來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微去旅行一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納˙托庫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上是需要安靜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是要走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你察覺到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 我是這個國家的國師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下總算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這個時間了 在幹些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 請稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這回事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在玩什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去旅行喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柚 小神 也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起旅行 真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓在下也同行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 隨你們便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下!! ！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉!! ！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝納威 柚葉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他逃了…讓他逃了…讓他逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他逃了…讓他逃了…讓他逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好天氣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊…沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的山…真高呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地…地面…真是凹凸不平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個只是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我…誤會什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上 卡露拉拜託我支援納˙托庫的叛亂軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有一點強迫性質
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過既沒做過什麼 也沒被怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…但是…我並不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓重要的人就這樣產生誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 艾露露對於我來說是重要的家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆庫魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 到裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 東霞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是迪利霍萊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是統率叛亂軍「卡露拉阿滋雷」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉阿滋雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是靠打仗維持生計的旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這裡發生了戰事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想請您僱傭我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是僱傭兵麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有來歷不明的人插手的份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的弟弟說了不需要我們的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不否定啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 東霞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 卡托瑪烏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是卡露拉阿滋雷大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遵守約定了呢 把那孩子撫養到這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝誇獎 我愧不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 也要把這件事告訴迪利霍萊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫卡露拉阿滋雷的女人已經不存在於這個世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我只是一個名叫卡露拉的 普通的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我殺 一個都別放過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這裡會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照約定…請讓我見妻兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 讓你們見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去見在黃泉等著你的妻兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺!! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤…撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔姆 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡托瑪烏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…只是…想和妻兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是背叛者應有的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…面對死者為何還要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 對不起 手滑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小男人一個 被人背叛是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有站在弱者的立場上考慮過事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 身為吉利亞基納族的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs48\fsp-1}註：吉利亞基納族：戰鬥能力十分突出的種族。擁有為了戰鬥而強化的身體，\N沒有固定的戰鬥方式也是其特徵。曾經一度繁榮，但是現在只有少數倖存者了。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要站在弱者的立場上考慮事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉利亞基納族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個因為依仗著強大而不知體會弱者痛苦的傲慢一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因此招致滅亡的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 即便你是末裔 但也是吉利亞基納族的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許你再這樣侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 看來再和你多說什麼你也明白不了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓你親身體會一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為弱者的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣 居然說要和我迪利霍萊交手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 為什麼不擺架勢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是什麼都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉利亞基納族人是不需要什麼架勢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉…不 各位旅行中的傭兵閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必助我們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡托瑪烏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己站得起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍萊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於回到我的身邊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深愛的人


